h1_title: Best Settings on PS5 and PC
content: Texture quality, not only has very little impact on performance but also doesn’t seem to degrade as you go to the lower setting. For that reason, we recommend putting it on Very High as there seems to be almost no negative effects to doing so.
promot:
This is an excerpt from the file 'Best_Settings_on_PS5_and_PC.md', within the main section titled 'Best Settings on PS5 and PC'.
The content is as follows:
Texture quality, not only has very little impact on performance but also doesn’t seem to degrade as you go to the lower setting. For that reason, we recommend putting it on Very High as there seems to be almost no negative effects to doing so.
